FBIS4-15505 "drsov068_a_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-068 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Kostikov Suggests Linking PFP, G-7 Membership Kostikov Suggests Linking PFP, G-7 Membership AU0804082294 Paris AFP in English 0812 GMT 8 Apr 94 AU0804082294 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Moscow, April 8 (AFP) -- Russia wants to link its joining the NATO Partnership for Peace [PFP] to joining the G-7 group of industrial nations, presidency spokesman Viacheslav Kostikov said. "If we are invited into the political and military partnership, it would be logical to make an approach in the economic sphere," he told reporters. "Russia would like to join the G-7. Why not link the two problems," he added.
